,"#institutional-adoption",[149],{"type":28,"value":150},"Institutional Adoption",{"type":23,"tag":24,"props":152,"children":153},{},[154],{"type":28,"value":155},"A wave of institutional adoption has been especially noticeable in recent weeks. Major trading firms have started using Solana's infrastructure for high-frequency trading operations, attracted by:",{"type":23,"tag":84,"props":157,"children":158},{},[159,164,176],{"type":23,"tag":88,"props":160,"children":161},{},[162],{"type":28,"value":163},"Transaction finality times of under a second",{"type":23,"tag":88,"props":165,"children":166},{},[167,169,174],{"type":28,"value":168},"Minimal fees averaging ",{"type":23,"tag":31,"props":170,"children":171},{},[172],{"type":28,"value":173},"$0.00025",{"type":28,"value":175}," per transaction",{"type":23,"tag":88,"props":177,"children":178},{},[179,181],{"type":28,"value":180},"Stable daily trading volumes exceeding ",{"type":23,"tag":31,"props":182,"children":183},{},[184],{"type":28,"value":185},"$1.5 billion",{"type":23,"tag":53,"props":187,"children":189},{"id":188},"real-world-asset-tokenization",[190],{"type":23,"tag":58,"props":191,"children":193},{"href":192},"#real-world-asset-tokenization",[194],{"type":28,"value":195},"Real-World Asset Tokenization",{"type":23,"tag":24,"props":197,"children":198},{},[199,201,206,208,213,215,220],{"type":28,"value":200},"Projects such as ",{"type":23,"tag":31,"props":202,"children":203},{},[204],{"type":28,"value":205},"Maple Finance",{"type":28,"value":207}," and ",{"type":23,"tag":31,"props":209,"children":210},{},[211],{"type":28,"value":212},"Credix",{"type":28,"value":214}," are pioneering institutional lending solutions on Solana, attracting participants from traditional finance. These platforms have collectively processed more than ",{"type":23,"tag":31,"props":216,"children":217},{},[218],{"type":28,"value":219},"$2.8 billion",{"type":28,"value":221}," in loans.",{"type":23,"tag":53,"props":223,"children":225},{"id":224},"technological-improvements",[226],{"type":23,"tag":58,"props":227,"children":229},{"href":228},"#technological-improvements",[230],{"type":28,"value":231},"Technological Improvements",{"type":23,"tag":24,"props":233,"children":234},{},[235,237,242],{"type":28,"value":236},"The recent introduction of compressed NFTs and state compression has reduced storage costs by ",{"type":23,"tag":31,"props":238,"children":239},{},[240],{"type":28,"value":241},"99%",{"type":28,"value":243},", opening up new possibilities in gaming and social applications.",{"type":23,"tag":53,"props":245,"children":247},{"id":246},"development-outlook",[248],{"type":23,"tag":58,"props":249,"children":251},{"href":250},"#development-outlook",[252],{"type":28,"value":253},"Development Outlook",{"type":23,"tag":24,"props":255,"children":256},{},[257,259,264],{"type":28,"value":258},"The current momentum suggests that Solana's DeFi ecosystem could reach ",{"type":23,"tag":31,"props":260,"children":261},{},[262],{"type":28,"value":263},"$12 billion",{"type":28,"value":265}," in TVL by mid-2024, especially if institutional adoption continues at its current pace. The combination of low costs, fast transactions, and growing institutional adoption creates a compelling proposition for users.",{"title":7,"searchDepth":267,"depth":267,"links":268},2,[269,270,271,272,273],{"id":55,"depth":267,"text":63},{"id":143,"depth":267,"text":150},{"id":188,"depth":267,"text":195},{"id":224,"depth":267,"text":231},{"id":246,"depth":267,"text":253},"markdown","content:crypto:post_lz1yw780-en.md","content","crypto\u002Fpost_lz1yw780-en.md","crypto\u002Fpost_lz1yw780-en","md",null,[282,290,296],{"_path":283,"title":284,"lead":285,"rubric":5,"author":286,"date":287,"cover":288,"readingTime":289},"\u002Fcrypto\u002Fmetodologiya-yldx-upravlenie-riskom","Риск в DeFi — не лотерея, а математика: методология YLDX","В 2022 году из DeFi украли $3.2 млрд — почти 6% всего рынка. Но риск в пуле ликвидности можно посчитать заранее и разложить так, что провал одного пула превращается из катастрофы в царапину. Разбираем методологию, по которой фонд YLDX выбирает пулы, делит капитал и ограничивает потери.","Редакция","2026-07-13","\u002Fcovers\u002Fyldx-risk.svg",5,{"_path":291,"title":292,"lead":293,"rubric":5,"author":286,"date":294,"cover":295,"readingTime":267},"\u002Fcrypto\u002Fsamostoyatelnoe-hranenie","«Не твои ключи — не твои монеты»: как на самом деле работает самостоятельное хранение","Криптовалюта не лежит в кошельке — она записана в блокчейне. Кошелёк хранит только ключ. Разбираем, что это значит на практике и почему одна ошибка при копировании адреса может стоить всех денег.","2026-07-08","\u002Fcovers\u002Fself-custody.svg",{"_path":297,"title":298,"lead":299,"rubric":5,"author":286,"date":300,"cover":301,"readingTime":267},"\u002Fcrypto\u002Flikvidnost-prostymi-slovami","Ликвидность простыми словами: почему в DeFi она решает всё","Пулы ликвидности заменили биржевой стакан математической формулой. Объясняем, как работает автоматический маркетмейкер, откуда берётся доходность поставщиков ликвидности и за что они на самом деле получают комиссию.","2026-06-28","\u002Fcovers\u002Fliquidity.svg",1784155999001]